plot: Gina, Heather and Emily whisk Shannon away for a relaxing girls' trip in La Quinta, only for Gina to find herself in quite the mess with Emily and Heather. Meanwhile, Tamra, Katie and Jenn head to Tamra's Big Bear house, where they dip their toes in the snow and some pie. Katie shares with the ladies that she feels set up by Gina, while Alexis reveals more trouble is heading Shannon's way.
